        <abstract>This is mainly a stylistc study. However, it contains a comprehensive research
                history of the sites in the Jinan region. The author does not talk about the lost
                sutra passage at Huangshi Ya, as he is only concerned with sculpture and their
                classification according to style. He also treats Shentong Si Qianfoya.</abstract>
